kernel-uek
[3.8.13-118.20.6]
- perf/hwbp: Simplify the perf-hwbp code, fix documentation (Linus Torvalds)  [Orabug: 27947608]  {CVE-2018-100199}

[3.8.13-118.20.5]
- x86/microcode: probe CPU features on microcode update (Ankur Arora)  [Orabug: 27806667] 
